Okrem toho, morský vánok je fajn.

235
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,880
Prečo sa tak ponáhľate do hotela?

236
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:48,060
Prečo si nesadneme a neporozprávame sa?

237
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,880
Dobre. Poďme si na chvíľu sadnúť.

238
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:50,840
Poďme.

239
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:03,050
Víťazný tím navrhuje,

240
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,280
aby si porazený tím vybral pravdu či odvahu.

241
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,040
Môžeš si vybrať len pravdu alebo odvahu.

242
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:10,280
Takže? Kto bude prvý?

243
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:16,280
Xin Ya, Qing Qing by mala byť potrestaná za svoj tím.

244
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,960
Nakoniec to kvôli nej stratil tím toľko bodov.

245
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,520
Čo si myslíš?

246
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,880
Myslím...

247
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,040
Mám nápad.

248
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,000
Xiao Feng?

249
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:27,920
Ja udelím tento trest.

250
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:31,320
Všetci ste moji kamaráti.

251
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:36,840
Je niečo, čo už nechcem skrývať.

252
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:39,630
Dúfam, že to všetci pochopíte.

253
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,680
Obzvlášť Xin Ya.

254
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,480
Brat Feng.

255
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,420
Chen Qing Qing.

256
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,980
Tu je tvoj trest.

257
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,550
Buď mojou priateľkou.

258
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:11,000
Si Tu Feng, takto sa to nerobí.

259
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:15,090
Čo sa deje? Chceš byť mojou priateľkou?

260
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,160
Áno.

261
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,760
Dovoľ, aby som ťa predstavil.

262
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:27,600
Toto je moje dievča, Chen Qing Qing.

263
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,990
Qing Qing, prečo si mi to nepovedala?

264
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:36,600
V poslednej dobe sme toho veľa zažili.

265
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,240
Dostali sme sa až na pokraj,

266
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:40,200
aby sme boli spolu.

267
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,840
- Gratulujem.
- Gratulujem.

268
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,960
Až do dna.

269
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,660
Baby, gratulujem.

270
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,720
Prosím, nikomu to nehovorte.

271
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:54,360
Sme rodina. Nechajme si to pre seba.

272
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:56,040
Xin Ya, si v poriadku?

273
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,050
Neplač.

274
00:14:58,160 --> 00:15:00,840
Viem, že si pre Si Tu Fenga veľa urobila.

275
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:03,950
Ale nikdy sa na teba nepozrel.

276
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,720
Si Tu Feng!

277
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:11,030
Vždy som ťa mala rada!

278
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:14,730
Nevedel si to?

279
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:19,080
Sľúbil si, že sa o mňa navždy postaráš.
Zabudol si na to?

280
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:21,730
Xin Ya, nerozumieš tomu.

281
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,640
Sľúbil som, že sa o teba postarám.

282
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:25,940
Ale len ako o mladšiu sestru.

283
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:29,560
Xiao Feng, Xin Ya pri tebe stála toľko rokov.

284
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:31,360
Vôbec sa ti nepáčila?

285
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:34,150
Nikdy si k nej nič necítil?

286
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:36,560
Dosť.

287
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:41,040
Skontrolujem ju.

288
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:54,960
Lan Xin Ya.

289
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,700
Čo robíš?

290
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,800
Snažíš sa mi smiať?

291
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,540
Lan Xin Ya, upokoj sa.

292
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,640
Je to len muž.

293
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,330
Prekonáš to.

294
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:10,170
V tvojom živote je to len malá prekážka.
Počuješ ma?

295
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:12,680
Ak nie je brat Feng so mnou,

296
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:17,330
tak radšej nechcem žiť.

297
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,440
Xin Ya.

298
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,160
Lan Xin Ya.

299
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:27,420
Xin Ya, otvor dvere!

300
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:30,370
Lan Xin Ya, otvor dvere!

301
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:32,880
Xin Ya.

302
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:56,640
Si Tu Feng, rýchlo choď za Xin You.

303
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:59,160
Nemala večeru. Tak som jej chcela niečo zaniesť.

304
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:01,400
Klopala som na dvere, ale neodpovedala.

305
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,800
Spýtala som sa na recepcii. Nikto ju
nevidel odchádzať z hotela.

306
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:06,420
Čože? Poďme sa pozrieť.

307
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,960
Čo urobíme?

308
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,800
Xin Ya!

309
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,840
Xin Ya!

310
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:12,360
Xin Ya!

311
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,720
Si Tu Feng, čo sa deje?

312
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:17,720
Chen Qing Qing, modli sa, aby bola v poriadku.

313
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:21,870
Ak sa niečo stane so Xin You, neodpustím ti.

314
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:26,040
Ustúpte. Manažér otvorí dvere.

315
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,790
Pane, táto izba.

316
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:31,680
Hej!

317
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,080
- Xin Ya!
- Xin Ya!

318
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,000
Zobuď sa.

319
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:37,520
Čo sa deje?

320
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,160
Tabletky na spanie.

321
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,960
Qing Qing, ako je na tom?

322
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:46,290
Stále má pulz. Rýchlo ju vezmime do nemocnice.

323
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,610
Otvorte dvere.

324
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,000
Idem.

325
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:52,960
Chen Qing Qing, nerob už ďalšie problémy.

326
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:57,480
Ak by si tu nebola, takéto niečo by sa nestalo.

327
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:04,280
Doktor, je moja dcéra v poriadku?

328
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,250
Nebojte sa.

329
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:08,440
Pacientka je stabilizovaná.

330
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:10,160
Potrebuje odpočinok.

331
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:12,210
Prosím, nerušte ju.

332
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,160
Okej.

333
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,920
Haló, dedko?

334
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:42,040
Prečo mi voláš tak skoro?

335
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,840
Pracoval si až do noci?

336
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,760
Nie.

337
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:50,270
Nemohol som spať, pretože si mi chýbala.

338
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:53,720
Qing Qing, kde teraz si?

339
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:54,840
Ja?

340
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:59,400
Som s kamarátmi.

341
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,120
Čo sa deje, dedko?

342
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:05,000
Znovu si začal kašľať?

343
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,400
Nie, som v poriadku.

344
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:10,280
Mám choré hrdlo, to je celé.

345
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:11,360
Dedko.

346
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:14,480
Neklam mi ako trojročnému decku.

347
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:16,590
Znovu si ochorel?

348
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:17,880
Kde si?

349
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,680
Som doma.

350
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:21,120
Počkaj na mňa, dedko.

351
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:23,360
Kúpim si letenku a hneď idem domov.

352
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:25,980
Počkaj ma. Čoskoro sa vrátim.

353
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:41,120
Lan Xin Ya.

354
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:43,260
Je v poriadku?

355
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,540
Bude v poriadku.

356
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:47,760
Vypumpovali jej žalúdok.

357
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:52,280
Doktor povedal, že len potrebuje byť pár dní hospitalizovaná.

358
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:54,080
To rada počujem.

359
00:19:54,080 --> 00:19:56,190
Práve mi volal dedko.

360
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,400
Ochorel.

361
00:19:57,400 --> 00:20:01,000
Preto sa musím ihneď vrátiť do Jinchengu.

362
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,080
Dobre.

363
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:08,320
Dobre sa o svojho dedka postaraj.

364
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:14,840
Mala by som ísť. Postaraj sa o Lan Xin Yu.

365
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,040
Okej.

366
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,320
- Qing Qing?
- Áno?

367
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,110
Vráť sa skoro.

368
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:32,840
Okej.

369
00:20:36,280 --> 00:20:37,600
Budeš mi chýbať.

370
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,560
Aj ty mne.

371
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:43,010
Už idem.

372
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,960
[Lokácia: Jingchen]

373
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,720
Pane, môžete ísť rýchlejšie?

374
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,560
Dobre.

375
00:21:19,280 --> 00:21:20,160
Dedko.

376
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,560
Prišla som ťa pozrieť.

377
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,760
Xin Ya.

378
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:42,440
Ako ti je? Je ti lepšie?

379
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,370
Chceš vodu?

380
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:52,160
Xin Ya.

